#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Veḷudvāravagga"
msgstr "1. At Bamboo Gate"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Dutiyasāriputtasutta"
msgstr "5. With Sāriputta (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.5:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ "
"sāriputtaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Sāriputta went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The "
"Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn55.5:1.2"
msgid "“‘sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ, sotāpattiyaṅgan’ti hidaṃ, sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sāriputta, they speak of a ‘factor of stream-entry’."

msgctxt "sn55.5:1.3"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, sāriputta, sotāpattiyaṅgan”ti?"
msgstr "What is a factor of stream-entry?”"

msgctxt "sn55.5:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Sappurisasaṃsevo hi, bhante, sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ, saddhammassavanaṃ "
"sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ, yonisomanasikāro sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ, dhammānudhammappaṭipatti "
"sotāpattiyaṅgan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the factors of stream-entry are associating with good people, "
"listening to the true teaching, proper attention, and practicing in line "
"with the teaching.”"

msgctxt "sn55.5:1.5"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

msgctxt "sn55.5:1.6"
msgid ""
"Sappurisasaṃsevo hi, sāriputta, sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ, saddhammassavanaṃ "
"sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ, yonisomanasikāro sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ, dhammānudhammappaṭipatti "
"sotāpattiyaṅgaṃ."
msgstr ""
"For the factors of stream-entry are associating with good people, listening "
"to the true teaching, proper attention, and practicing in line with the "
"teaching."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.5:2.1"
msgid "‘Soto, soto’ti hidaṃ, sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "Sāriputta, they speak of ‘the stream’."

msgctxt "sn55.5:2.2"
msgid "Katamo nu kho, sāriputta, soto”ti?"
msgstr "What is the stream?”"

msgctxt "sn55.5:2.3"
msgid "“Ayameva hi, bhante, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo soto, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“Sir, the stream is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn55.5:2.4"
msgid ""
"sammādiṭṭhi, sammāsaṅkappo, sammāvācā, sammākammanto, sammāājīvo, "
"sammāvāyāmo, sammāsati, sammāsamādhī”ti."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion.”"

msgctxt "sn55.5:2.5"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

msgctxt "sn55.5:2.6"
msgid "Ayameva hi, sāriputta, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo soto, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "For the stream is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn55.5:2.7"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.348"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.5:3.1"
msgid "‘Sotāpanno, sotāpanno’ti hidaṃ, sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "Sāriputta, they speak of ‘a stream-enterer’."

msgctxt "sn55.5:3.2"
msgid "Katamo nu kho, sāriputta, sotāpanno”ti?"
msgstr "What is a stream-enterer?”"

msgctxt "sn55.5:3.3"
msgid ""
"“Yo hi, bhante, iminā ariyena aṭṭhaṅgikena maggena samannāgato ayaṃ vuccati "
"sotāpanno, svāyaṃ āyasmā evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, anyone who possesses this noble eightfold path is called a stream-"
"enterer, the venerable of such and such name and clan.”"

msgctxt "sn55.5:3.4"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

msgctxt "sn55.5:3.5"
msgid ""
"Yo hi, sāriputta, iminā ariyena aṭṭhaṅgikena maggena samannāgato ayaṃ "
"vuccati sotāpanno, svāyaṃ āyasmā evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto”ti."
msgstr ""
"For anyone who possesses this noble eightfold path is called a stream-"
"enterer, the venerable of such and such name and clan.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.5:3.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
